    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "@dhayab i have tried making your example work with multiple indexes but resultsByIndex always contains data for indexName added on the `<InstantSearch indexName=\"test_inject_content\">` and not the `<Index indexName=\"test_product\">.` \r\n\r\n```\r\ngetHits: ({ position, resultsByIndex }) => {\r\n     const index = position / 5;\r\n     const item =\r\n         resultsByIndex.instant_search &&\r\n          resultsByIndex.instant_search.hits[index];\r\n\r\n     return item ? [item] : [];\r\n},\r\n```\r\n\r\nAny help here would be appreciated! ",
