    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Is there any other way to do it custom by transforming the response and adding in the custom rule attributes for custom promotional tiles or other information? \r\n\r\nSince we show 20 products, when we add a promotional tile via a rule, we want to show only 19 products to keep the layout at the bottom of the page consistent. \r\n\r\nFeature would be very useful for a lot of our ecommerce clients.\r\n",
