  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "If you want to inject banners in a static position, I recommend an approach like https://www.algolia.com/doc/guides/managing-results/rules/merchandising-and-promoting/how-to/add-banners/ and inject it manually when you use `useHits` into the right position of the `items` list. ",
